skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my sensei
des: My Sensei is a skill that you can always some to for a great quote to uplift your spirits. Once the app is started you can ask My Sensei to say a quote or give you wisdom and it will respond with a random quote for you. More quotes will be added weekly.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
